You have (6) options
Press 1 to List the contents of a directory provided by the user
Press 2 to List the contents of a directory provided by the user as well as all of its sub directories.
Press 3 to Locate a file with a given name.
Press 4 to Locate files with a given file extension
Press 5 to Concatenate the contents of 2 files whose names are provided by the user and output the result to a third file 
Press 6 to Exit
